posts.text:
To embrace the world wide celebration of World Statistics Day 2015, [CBS (Statistics Netherlands)] (http://www.cbs.nl/) and the [Netherlands Society for Statistics and Operations Research (VvS+OR)] (http://www.vvs-or.nl/) collaborated to produce a video that showcases the so-called CBS's Compass that monitors Quality of Life on three different dashboards. These are the actual quality of life, quality of life in the future, and quality of life world-wide. The video is in Dutch;  

 [![CBS (Statistics Netherlands)](img/posts/Netherlands_video.jpg)](https://youtu.be/fRoKnABqAL0)

 A version in English is envisioned for the near future.
